---
export const prerender = true;
import BlogLayout from '../../layouts/BlogLayout.astro';
import '../../styles/global.css';
---

<BlogLayout
  title="Scrabble Words With Double F — SCAFFOLD, DAFFODIL, OFFHAND & More"
  description="Best double-F words for Scrabble. SCAFFOLD (16pts), DAFFODIL (15pts), OFFHAND (17pts). FF pattern strategy for high-value plays. Free word finder."
  keywords="scrabble double f words, scaffold scrabble, daffodil scrabble, offhand scrabble, ff words scrabble, double f strategy, double letter words"
>
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org", "@type": "Article",
    "headline": "Scrabble Words With Double F — SCAFFOLD, DAFFODIL, OFFHAND & More",
    "description": "Best double-F Scrabble words. FF pattern strategy for high-value plays.",
    "datePublished": "2026-06-30",
    "author": { "@type": "Organization", "name": "ScrabbleWordsFinder.com", "url": "https://www.scrabblewordsfinder.com" },
    "publisher": { "@type": "Organization", "name": "ScrabbleWordsFinder.com" },
    "mainEntityOfPage": { "@type": "WebPage", "@id": "https://www.scrabblewordsfinder.com/blog/scrabble-words-with-double-f" }
  })} />
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org", "@type": "FAQPage",
    "mainEntity": [
      { "@type": "Question", "name": "What are the highest scoring double-F words?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "OFFHAND (17pts), SCAFFOLD (16pts), and DAFFODIL (15pts). Each F is worth 4 points, giving FF pairs 8 base points." } },
      { "@type": "Question", "name": "How many F tiles are in Scrabble?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Only 2 F tiles (4pts each). Drawing both gives 8 points from F alone — among the highest-value double combinations." } },
      { "@type": "Question", "name": "What short FF words are valid?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "OFF (6pts), IFF (6pts), EFF (6pts), TOFF (7pts). JIFFY (18pts) and TAFFY (11pts) add premium letters for bigger scores." } }
    ]
  })} />

  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <article class="prose prose-invert prose-gray max-w-none">
      <nav class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-6 not-prose flex items-center gap-1">
        <a href="/blog/" class="hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">← Blog</a><span class="mx-1">›</span><span class="text-gray-300">Word Lists</span>
      </nav>
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Scrabble Words With Double F — SCAFFOLD, DAFFODIL, OFFHAND & More</h1>
      <div class="not-prose mb-8 flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-400">
        <time datetime="2026-06-30">June 30, 2026</time><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-gray-600"></span><span>4 min read</span><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-gray-600"></span>
        <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-blue-400 hover:underline"><span aria-hidden="true">🔤</span> Word Finder</a>
      </div>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-300 mb-8">Each F tile is worth 4 points — double that with FF and you get 8 points before any other letters count. With only 2 F tiles in the bag, drawing both is rare but the scoring payoff is substantial.</p>

      <div class="not-prose my-6 p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-6 text-center">
          <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">17 pts</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">OFFHAND</p></div>
          <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">16 pts</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">SCAFFOLD</p></div>
          <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">15 pts</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">DAFFODIL</p></div>
          <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">8 pts</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Per FF pair</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">Top Double-F Words</h2>

      <div class="not-prose my-8 p-6 rounded-2xl border-2 border-amber-500/50 bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-950/30 to-yellow-950/20 relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute top-3 right-4 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-amber-500/70">👑 Top FF Word</div>
        <p class="text-2xl font-black text-white tracking-wider mb-2">OFFHAND — 17 Points</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-amber-300 font-semibold mb-3">O=1, F=4, F=4, H=4, A=1, N=1, D=2 · 7 letters · Bingo eligible</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">Three 4-point tiles (F, F, H) power this word. With the bingo bonus, OFFHAND scores 67 total points.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="not-prose my-6 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10"><p class="text-amber-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">🏗️ SCAFFOLD</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">16 pts · 8 letters · C=3 + FF + D=2</p></div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10"><p class="text-amber-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">🌼 DAFFODIL</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">15 pts · 8 letters · D=2 pair + FF</p></div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10"><p class="text-amber-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">⚡ JIFFY</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">18 pts · 5 letters · J=8 + FF + Y=4</p></div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10"><p class="text-amber-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">☕ COFFEE</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">14 pts · 6 letters · C=3 + FF mid-game</p></div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">FF Pattern Strategy</h2>

      <div class="not-prose my-6 grid grid-cols-1 gap-4">
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors"><p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">OFF- prefix is gold:</span> OFFHAND, OFFLOAD, OFFENCE — the OFF- start guarantees 9+ points. Look for this pattern with both F tiles.</p></div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors"><p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">-IFF and -AFF endings:</span> STIFF (11pts), STAFF (11pts), CLIFF (13pts) — short words that score well in tight positions.</p></div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors"><p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">Target premium squares:</span> F on DLS doubles to 8 per tile. Both F's on doubles gives 16 from FF alone.</p></div>
      </div>

      <div class="not-prose my-6 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-3">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">STAFF</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">11pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">CLIFF</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">13pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">EFFECT</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">14pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">BUFFALO</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">15pts</span></span>
      </div>

      <div class="not-prose my-6 p-5 rounded-xl border border-blue-500/30 bg-blue-950/20">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-blue-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">💡 Value Insight</p>
        <p class="text-base text-gray-200">FF contributes <span class="text-white font-medium">8 points</span> per word — the most valuable playable same-letter double after ZZ (20pts).</p>
      </div>

      <aside class="border-t border-gray-800 mt-12 pt-8 not-prose">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Related Articles</h3>
        <div class="grid gap-3">
          <a href="/blog/scrabble-words-with-double-l/" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group"><span class="text-blue-500 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform">→</span><span class="text-sm text-gray-300 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Scrabble Words With Double L</span></a>
          <a href="/blog/scrabble-words-with-double-z/" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group"><span class="text-blue-500 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform">→</span><span class="text-sm text-gray-300 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Scrabble Words With Double Z</span></a>
        
          <a href="/blog/scrabble-words-with-double-n/" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group"><span class="text-blue-500 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform">→</span><span class="text-sm text-gray-300 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Scrabble Words With Double N</span></a>

          <a href="/blog/scrabble-words-with-double-r/" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group"><span class="text-blue-500 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform">→</span><span class="text-sm text-gray-300 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Scrabble Words With Double R</span></a>
</div>
      </aside>

      <div class="not-prose mt-10 p-5 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-900/20 to-cyan-900/20 border border-blue-800 rounded-xl shadow-sm">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4 flex-wrap">
          <p class="text-sm text-blue-300 font-medium">🔤 Find double-F words from your rack — free Scrabble solver, instant results</p>
          <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white text-sm font-semibold transition-colors shadow-sm">Open Word Finder →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="not-prose mt-8 text-center"><a href="/blog/" class="text-sm text-gray-400 hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">← Back to all articles</a></div>
    </article>
  </div>
</BlogLayout>
